race.comment: THE MERCENARY (2) finished fifth last start over 2050m at this track, beaten 6 metres. Best recent result was a win at this track three starts ago over 2050m. No excuses from this advantageous draw. Good enough to put himself in the winners' stall. GOTA GOOD WARHOL (3) finished third last start over 1177m at Pinjarra, beaten 2.5 metres, after scoring at the previous appearance over 2050m at this track. Will enjoy a nice run from this favourable starting position. Finds a suitable assignment and can play a significant role. I SEE FIRE (1) is on the radar after his last-start fifth over 2100m at Bunbury nine days ago. HUGHEY (4) is better than his last-start eighth over 2050m at this track. Each way value if he can find the front early on.
